name: CASH.
description: I met Cash briefly while he was working security outside a building on Louisiana St. I spoke to him and his coworker, took a quick portrait of the each of them, and had them write. When Cash gave me back the notebook he was laughing a bit. I wasn't sure why since I don't read these pages before I walk away from the person. When I looked and saw "smoke good dope" written I just laughed. That made the whole interaction for me.
